tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE music_therapy_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  intervention_type VARCHAR(100),
  mental_health_condition VARCHAR(100),
  effectiveness_rating INT,
  therapy_duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE patient_data (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  therapy_intervention_id INT,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
  FOREIGN KEY (therapy_intervention_id) REFERENCES therapy_interventions(intervention_id)
);

CREATE TABLE therapy_interventions (
 intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
 mental_health_condition VARCHAR(255),
 effectiveness_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
 feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 patient_id INT,
 intervention_id INT,
 feedback_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE therapist_data (
 therapist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 therapist_name VARCHAR(255),
 therapy_type VARCHAR(255),
 experience_years INT
)

CREATE TABLE music_therapy_interventions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
    mental_health_condition VARCHAR(255),
    effectiveness_rating FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE intervention_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    effectiveness_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    mental_health_condition VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE therapists (
    therapist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    therapist_name VARCHAR(255),
    specialization VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE patient_data (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    condition_id INT,
    intervention_id INT,
    therapy_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE therapy_ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    intervention_id INT,
    rating_score FLOAT,
    feedback TEXT
);
